  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `SemanticSearchControl.tsx` lines ~510-525 (where `boundSearchIndexName` is currently set from `context.parameters.searchIndexName?.raw`). Note the consumption sites: `useSemanticSearch(apiService, searchScope, scopeId, boundSearchIndexName)` and the `boundSearchIndexName` pass to NavigationService at ~line 779.</step>
    <step order="2">Add private async method `resolveSearchIndexNameAsync(context: ComponentFramework.Context&lt;IInputs&gt;): Promise&lt;string | null&gt;` per spec §5 pseudocode. Wraps the Xrm.WebApi call in try/catch returning null on failure.</step>
    <step order="3">In `init()` or wherever `boundSearchIndexName` is currently derived, change from synchronous read of bound property to async resolution. Store in component state (`React.useState&lt;string | null&gt;`). Re-render dependent components when resolution completes. Since this is React 16, use a state-setter pattern (not React 18 transitions).</step>
    <step order="4">Remove `&lt;property name="searchIndexName" ...&gt;` element from `ControlManifest.Input.xml`. Verify all references to `context.parameters.searchIndexName` are removed (manifest types will need regen — `npm run refreshTypes`).</step>
    <step order="5">5-location version bump 1.1.74 → 1.1.75: (a) `ControlManifest.Input.xml` `version` attribute + description `(v1.1.75)`; (b) main component footer string in `SemanticSearchControl.tsx`; (c) `Solution/solution.xml` `&lt;Version&gt;`; (d) `Solution/Controls/.../ControlManifest.xml` `version` + description; (e) `Solution/pack.ps1` `$version`.</step>
    <step order="6">Update unit tests in `__tests__/`: tests that mock `context.parameters.searchIndexName` are obsolete; replace with tests that mock `context.webAPI.retrieveRecord` returning the expanded record shape. Update `NavigationService.test.ts` if it tested with PCF-bound input.</step>
    <step order="7">`npm run build:prod` (NOT `npm run build`). Verify bundle size &lt; 1 MB (per pcf-deploy skill expectations).</step>
    <step order="8">Run code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5 (FULL rigor). Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 106 🔲 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

